<li><strong>Vendor (Bob):</strong> Needs an intuitive interface to add products, process orders, and manage inventory. Highly values the AI Product Description Generator to save time.</li>
<li><strong>Business Analyst (Charlie):</strong> Requires access to deep analytics, AI Sales Analytics, and custom reporting tools to identify trends and present findings to management.</li>
