<h2>20. Process Flow Diagrams (Mermaid)</h2>
<p>```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Vendor Logs In] --&gt; B{Action?}
    B --&gt;|Add Product| C[Enter Basic Details]
    C --&gt; D[Click 'Generate AI Description']
    D --&gt; E[Backend calls OpenAI/Gemini]
    E --&gt; F[AI Returns Optimized Description]
    F --&gt; G[Vendor Reviews &amp; Saves]
    G --&gt; H[Saved to PostgreSQL]</p>
<pre><code>B --&gt;|View Dashboard| I[Load AI Sales Analytics]
I --&gt; J[Display Charts &amp; Insights]
</code></pre>
<p>```</p>
<hr />
<h2>21. High-Level Business Workflow</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong>Vendor Registration:</strong> Vendor signs up; Super Admin approves the account.</li>
<li><strong>Catalog Creation:</strong> Vendor utilizes the AI Product Description Generator to quickly build their catalog.</li>
<li><strong>Order Ingestion:</strong> Orders flow into the system from external storefronts.</li>
<li><strong>Fulfillment &amp; Inventory:</strong> Vendor processes orders. AI Inventory Forecasting alerts the vendor when stock is running low based on predictive trends.</li>
<li><strong>Customer Feedback:</strong> Reviews are ingested; AI Sentiment Analysis categorizes them into Positive/Neutral/Negative.</li>
<li><strong>Business Strategy:</strong> Vendors and Admins review the AI Business Recommendation Engine to optimize pricing and marketing.</li>
</ol>
